title: Validate Webui Feature flag "add_os_and_access_method_to_ssl_decryption" to enable new feature
custom_steps:
- Switch to Feature branch on local dev box or bring up new develop build on with changes for webUI and dpmgmtsvc
- Run Provisioner API to enable feature flag "feature flag: add_os_and_access_method_to_ssl_decryption" to 1.
- Review tenant database "global_var" table updated with new feature flag and set to 1
custom_expected:
- Provisioner API should return status sucess and no errors.
- Review tenant database "global_var" table updated with new feature flag and set to 1
